---
title: Golden Baked Parmesan Polenta Slice with Extra Chutney-Bacon Jam & Spring Onion Sprinkle
description: Skip the usual sides and indulge in our creamy, baked Polenta studded with sharp cheese and fresh spring onion. Crowned with a rich, sweet-and-savoury bacon jam, it’s a warming, golden-hued dish that brings comfort and cheer to your Christmas table.
